OL,4,CPrimary schools urged by campaigners to
OL,5,Ctackle gender stereotypes
OL,6, Calling girls "sweetie" or boys "mate"
OL,7, in primary school perpetuates gender
OL,8, stereotypes, campaigners say.
OL,10,FIn a letter to the education secretary
OL,11,Fin England, various groups are calling
OL,12,Fon the government to address the
OL,13,Flanguage and ideas used in schools.
OL,15,FStereotypes limit children's
OL,16,Faspirations and create inequalities
OL,17,Fthat help fuel gender-based violence,
OL,18,Fthey say.
OL,20,FThe government says challenging
OL,21,Fstereotypes is in its guidance.
